Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人怎麼回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:30.09,post@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(397,378)}給孩子以{\c&H3D07A0&}夢{\r}想—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:30.09,post@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(696,488)}成田芭蕾舞教室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:30.09,post@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(823,533)}暑期生募集中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好的就這樣繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是在為夢想而努力呢 有哪裡做錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你摸什麼魚啊 你這樣怎麼成得了偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是你的夢想嗎 給我更努力一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽…媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢 夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢 夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正不管我怎麼嚮往 也肯定當不了職業選手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 這樣根本入不了圍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本成不了畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天 我要和小心音一起去看電影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼人 我們去兜兜風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我實現一下我的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻把灰吹和月銀叫回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要啟動系統了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行 灰吹他…沒…沒有開機…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個笨蛋 都說要他開機了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個在響的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是小舞亞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡…是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要下車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家孩子怎麼可能成得了芭蕾舞演員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都胖成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家的孩子絕對會實現自己的夢想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 媽媽 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要成為偶像 不論發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我一定會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要成為第一人氣偶像…我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成為偶像 成為明星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被大家關注 站在閃閃發光的舞台上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想盡情地唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 現在也還不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 就是那個叫櫻子的人所說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要給我一個機會的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花嵐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:09.96,post -blue,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz2\pos(546,324)}臨時停業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:09.96,post -blue,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(578,626)}真的十分抱歉 請下次再來光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的機體的修理還沒有完成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻煩 稍微有點問題也還是能用的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們出擊吧 翼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…就由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花嵐？為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我也一起戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是突然就上陣……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你連訓練都沒做過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽君…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和她一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救世界 為此是否真的需要你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我認真傾聽一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deava系統 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector Outlane連結系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花嵐 花嵐 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪裡啊 花嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢…夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 要合體了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲合體 盛開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUARION
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢 夢 夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厲害嗎 小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 普通的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是無法對文字怪獸造成致命傷害的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 為了取勝還需要某樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須逃脫才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成為偶像 成為美麗閃耀的第一人氣偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須成為偶像 站到舞台上 為了大家而歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為偶像 成為№1的偶像 成為大家嚮往的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住口 我不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花嵐的精神值 正在急劇下降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 由我來代替她出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不允許 就算你搭乘受損Vector出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會改變現在的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為偶像 唱歌跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為無所不能的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我不想再聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你要聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後去看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個想要把你擊潰的 「夢」的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小花嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「白箱」門前出現的人的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種時候 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小花嵐的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓她進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音是需要有傳達的對象的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花嵐 你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來 花嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了 為了實現我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽想實現的並不是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是自己的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花嵐…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成為偶像的不是我 而是媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因為沒有實現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才把自己的夢想託付給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢！?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:18:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭蕾也是 真正想跳芭蕾的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是媽媽你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是媽媽的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是海風花嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是我 一個叫做海風花嵐的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和陽君那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼喚來了文字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該去發聲的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在應該發聲的時刻 所發出的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會賦予文字力量 改變現實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在正確的時間 在正確的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是創聲力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直沒有說出口的真正的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的夢想是虛幻縹緲的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但正因為這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才有在一瞬一秒上 賭上全部的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢 夢！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的夢想早就消失在彼方了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的對不起 花嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我用我的夢想將花嵐束縛了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我說我的夢想是想成為偶像 這個也不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成為聲優
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小舞亞還在繼續失聯呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真悠閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明自己做的文字怪獸被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NESTA創聲力研究所所長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林晉太郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 是小少爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過吧 不要這麼叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文字怪獸又不是我製造的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製造出它們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是將文字變成文字怪獸的你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒事 就來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個想要做的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次好像很認真的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然會認真起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是為了奪回舞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底該去哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月銀舞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在的話就趕快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月銀舞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能聽到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不到嗎 月銀舞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.09,0:21:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰吹陽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你的聲音 傳達到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹把通訊設備帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:21:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經把我的號碼輸進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在事情變麻煩之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我也會把電源打開的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口氣這麼大 你以為你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 我說 你們知道七夕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是五節之一嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.59,0:23:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短 短冊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:23:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短冊怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫 寫上願望的話有可能被實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:23:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 要把短冊掛到看著一帆風順的白領脖子上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我去掛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.90,0:24:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 射出吧 穿心之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.98,0:24:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬 敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,

